description:
Unique and urban apartment central in Oslo Located on central Greenland, which is a 10 minute walk from the Central Station, the Opera House and the Munch Museum. A stone's throw away from the subway station.

Convenient floor plan and decorative decor. The home includes living room, kitchen, one available bedroom and bath, and has an airy ceiling height up to 3.15 m. A cozy and practical home with a charming atmosphere.

The apartment is lavish with, among other things, a new kitchen in 2018. The color choices are light and harmonious.

name: Two bedroom apartment Grunerløkka
description:
Enjoy Oslo in this classic 2-bedroom apartment located in quiet neigborhood in Grunerløkka. It is walking distance to all of central Oslo, including grocery stores, lots of good resturants and cafes, shopping, tram, subway, bus, Oslo Central Station, as well as Sofienbergparken and Botanical Gardens.

The apartment includes a combined kitchen and living room, hall, bathroom and two bedrooms. There is a double bed in the main bedroom, and a 120cm bed in the other bedroom.
